materials_text: {"blocks":[{"key":"rqs9","text":"DABCO (in small fridge below oven; Sigma #D-2522)","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"2n3qk","text":"Polyvinyl Alcohol (in chemical bin#11; Sigma #D-8136)","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4knip","text":"Glycerol (in chemical bin #7; Sigma #G-9012)","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"1gl80","text":"0.2M Tris buffer @ pH 8.5 (12ml = 2.4ml 1M Tris + 9.6 ml double distilled water)","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3e8l5","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"5br9n","text":" 1.5 ml microcentrifuge tubes","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ikua","text":"90 ml centrifuge tubes (including tubes for balance)","type":"unordered-list-item","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

status.info: We use this protocol and it's working

steps.step: {"blocks":[{"key":"cmkhp","text":"Add 2.4 g of Polyvinyl Alcohol (Mol. Wt. 30,000-70,000) to 6ml of glycerol.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"key":0,"offset":13,"length":17},{"key":1,"offset":66,"length":8}],"data":{}},{"key":"aj679","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"link","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"guid":"89B5FF80A17E11ECAA01CFF43E9827D9","url":"https://www.sigmaaldrich.com/US/en/sds/sial/p8136"}},"1":{"type":"link","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"guid":"CFCD4410A17E11ECAA01CFF43E9827D9","url":"https://www.sigmaaldrich.com/US/en/sds/sial/g9012"}}}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"filr1","text":"Add 6ml of double distilled water and leave for at least 2 hours at room temperature (rotate overnight)","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"5v2ii","text":"Heat to 50° C for 10 minutes with occasional mixing. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"9nu1g","text":"After polyvinyl alcohol is dissolved, clarify by centrifugation (5000g = ~6800 rpm) for 15 minutes at 20° C.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"7tm24","text":"Collect supernatant liquid and measure amount collected. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"1ahc2","text":"Add DABCO to 2.5% as antifade medium:","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"hs5f","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"8j1c8","text":"2.5g DABCO / 100ml of liquid","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"2r847","text":"pH to 8.6 with pH paper (the paper will disintegrate, so pipette onto paper rather than putting paper into container). ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
{"blocks":[{"key":"2blok","text":"Aliquot in 0.5ml microcentrifuge tubes and store at -20° C. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}

{"blocks":[{"key":"4ie7n","text":"Stocks of Gelvatol are supposed to be stable at room temperature for several weeks after thawing. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{}}
